  <summary date="2016-02-04T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Fairness for Agricultural Machinery and Equipment Act

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to eliminate the placed-in-service restriction on the depreciation of certain farming business machinery and equipment and to make permanent the five-year recovery period for such property.</summary>
